{
  "texts": [
    "It is quite fine by me.",
    "But I wouldn't give this answer to my students because it doesn't enable them to reflect.",
    "[...] Reflection needs additional information, which is not simply an answer to the question. \"",
    "• The context added to an LLM query may be phrased in different ways, even when the same information is included.",
    "The evaluation of the phrasing's effect is important, but it presents a complex challenge."
  ]
}